<template>
    <el-table :data="tableData" stripe style="width: 100%">
        <el-table-column prop="date" label="课题名称" width="180">
        </el-table-column>
        <el-table-column prop="name" label="课题类型" width="180">
        </el-table-column>
        <el-table-column prop="address" label="课题来源">
        </el-table-column>
    </el-table>
</template>

<script>
export default {
    name: "TopicPreview",
    data() {
        return {
            tableData: [{
                date: '2016-05-02',
                name: '王小虎',
                address: '上海市普陀区金沙江路 1518 弄'
            }]
        }
    }
}
</script>
